<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL30">
<l>maṉattilōr tūymai yillai vāyilō riṉco lillai</l>
<l>ciṉattiṉāṟ ceṟṟam nōkkit tīviḷi viḷivaṉ vāḷā</l>
<l>puṉattuḻāy mālai yāṉē poṉṉicūḻ tiruva raṅkā</l>
<l>eṉakkiṉik katiyeṉ collā yeṉṉaiyā ḷuṭaiya kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no purity in [my] manas, no sweet words on [my] lips.</l>
<l>I uselessly utter fiery words out of anger, eyeing [the others] with hatred.</l>
<l>O You with garlands of basil from the uplands! O You of Śrīraṅgam surrounded by the Poṉṉi!</l>
<l>Tell [me]: what is henceforth my refuge? O King who rules over me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
